</tr>
<tr class="request-param">
<td>skip_confirmation</td>
<td>
</td>
<td>boolean</td>
<td class="param-desc">
<p>Only valid for site admins and account admins making requests; If true, the
channel is automatically validated and no confirmation email or SMS is
